OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FIt will be a largely dry day
OL,6,Fwith bright and sunny spells, the odd
OL,7,Fisolated shower possible however.
OL,8,FTurning cloudier in the evening with
OL,9,Frain spreading eastwards.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FMostly
OL,12,Fcloudy with outbreaks of rain on
OL,13,FSunday and Monday as winds strengthen,
OL,14,Fsome drier and brighter intervals
OL,15,Fpossible. Drier Tuesday with just the
OL,16,Fodd shower possible and sunny spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
